{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-311-biclinic-integral-quadrilaterals","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 311: Biclinicični potpuni četvorougaonosnik","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>$ABCD$ je četvorougaonik sa spoljnim uglovima, čije stranice imaju pune brojeve i $1 ≤ AB &#x3C; BC &#x3C; CD &#x3C; AD$.</p>\n<p>$BD$ ima dužinu punog broja. $O$ je u sredini $BD$-a. $AO$ ima dužinu punog broja.</p>\n<p>Naziva se $ABCD$ četvorostranični pravougaonik savršeno bicliničan ako $AO = CO ≤ BO = DO$.</p>\n<p>Na primer, sljedeći četvorustan je kompletan četvorustan biclinika: $AB = 19$, $BC = 29$, $CD = 37$, $AD = 43$, $BD = 48$ i $AO = CO = 23$.</p>\n<img alt=\"mstatili wa pande nne ABCD, na nukta O, katikati ya BD\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/biclinic-integral-quadrilaterals.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Neka je $B(N)$ broj pravougaonika sa četiri pune stranice biclinike različite $ABCD$ koje zadovoljavaju ${AB}^2 + {BC}^2 + {CD}^2 + {AD}^2 ≤ N$. Možemo dokazati da $B(10\\,000) = 49$ i $B(1\\,000\\,000) = 38239$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $B(10,,000,000,000)$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4a31000cf542c50ffb6","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301967,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-311-biclinic-integral-quadrilaterals"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function biclinicIntegralQuadrilaterals() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nbiclinicIntegralQuadrilaterals();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>biclinicIntegralQuadrilaterals()</code> treba vratiti <code>2466018557</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(biclinicIntegralQuadrilaterals(), 2466018557);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-311-biclinic-integral-quadrilaterals","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-312-cyclic-paths-on-sierpiski-graphs","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-310-nim-square","id":"5900f4a31000cf542c50ffb6","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-311-biclinic-integral-quadrilaterals"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}